text: He loka samajatata ki sain'ye adyapa geli nahita ani jara sain'ye parata ali tara he asi iccha balagatata ki te vanata rahanaryammadhye vanavasi lokansobata asate tara bare jhale asate yasathi ki tumaci khabara bata gheta rahile asate. Jara te tumacyata hajara asate (taridekhila?) Ugaca bolanyaca mana rakhanyasathi thodese ladhale asate
